<item>
            <title>[LU-16113] Update lock_page_memcg configure test</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16113</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Update lock_page_memcg configure test&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Newer kernels such as 5.16 fail the compile test with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ERROR: modpost: &quot;lock_page_memcg&quot; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;../build/conftest.ko&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; undefined!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Change the test so it does not require the modpost result.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Alternatively a dummy Module.symvers can be generated to&lt;br/&gt;
resolve the modpost failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See also current parallel build series which adds the ability to generate a dummy Module.symvers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
